Package: ReportManager
Title: R Application To Manage Parameterized Reports
Version: 0.8.5
Authors@R: c(person("Benjamin", "Nutter", email = "benjamin.nutter@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: This package provides a shiny application framework for managing 
  an organization's standardized reports. The application provides the infrastructure to 
  manage report reviews, approval, and submission to internal and external clients. 
Depends:
  R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports:
  checkmate (>= 1.8.0),
  DBI,
  odbc,
  shiny
Suggests:
